
# Project OVAL-GLASS: Macro-Scale Photonic Hardware Architecture
### An Open-Source Blueprint for Low-Cost, Continuous-Flow Computing

**IP, DESIGN & CONCEPT BY:** Victor M. G. G. (V.M.G.G.) aka KARTUNE  
**PROJECT LINE:** Toonz Nexus-9 / Project 76 Toonz  
**CORE ARCHITECTURE:** The KARTUNE Nested Oval-Glass Matrix  
